BUILD
______________________
1. Make sure skibare87/flaskhost:latest is available by building first or modify to reference the correct image

> ./build


RUN
______________________
1. The app folder is already included in this image, no need to add it
2. Modify your files volume to store files where you want

> docker run -v ./files:/files -p 8080:80 skibare87/flaskhost:latest
